1978;;Special Delivery;;Canadian;;Eunice Macauley, John Weldon;;;;nfb animated short;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special_Delivery_(1978_film);;After Ralph dismisses his wife's orders to clear the snow from the front walk before he went out for the day, he finds his regular mailman dead on his front stairs, having slipped on the ice and broken his neck. Fearing police investigations and potential wrongful death lawsuits from the letter carriers' union amongst other things, Ralph must go to great lengths to cover up the mailman's death while his wife comes to terms with her past.[2]